    "text": [
        "Dear Sam,",
        "I am writing this letter to inform about the my resignation from the duties that have been working past 3 years.",
        "I have decided to do my own business in my native place since it has been my long-term goal since my childhood. Although, the kind of business I would like to do is, not yet decided. I have a couple of ideas in my mind and even I am not sure which one I will take up form that long list of thoughts.",
        "Since day one of this project, I have keen to learn so my new initiatives and a plethora of skills, that will definitely helpful going forward for my professional as well as personal life, such as communication skills for the new business, customer satisfaction, team co-ordination, and team perseverance, irrespective of the nature of work we do. In addition to that,  I have learned ,how to behave as a quintessential human-being.",
        "However, I am requesting you to provide me the reference paper, probably that might immensely helpful for me in near future. There would no urgency to provide that letter since I do not have any appointment where I required to submit the letter of reference.",
        "Thank You so much for being supportive and keep motivating all the time.",
        "Regards",
